'''对甲苯磺酸'''（[[化学式|化学式]]：''p''-[[甲基|CH<sub>3</sub>]][[苯|C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>]][[磺酸|SO<sub>3</sub>H]]，也写作[[对甲苯磺酰基|Ts]]OH）是一个不具[[氧化性|氧化性]]的[[有机酸|有机强酸]]，酸性是[[苯甲酸|苯甲酸]]的一百万倍。白色针状或粉末结晶，易潮解，可溶于水、[[醇|醇]]和其他极性溶剂。会使纸张、木材等脱水发生[[碳化|碳化]]。常见的是对甲苯磺酸一水合物TsOH·H<sub>2</sub>O。

== 用途 ==
对甲苯磺酸是[[有机合成|有机合成]]常用的酸催化剂。用它与氢氧化钠中和制得对甲苯磺酸钠，再与[[五氯化磷|五氯化磷]]作用，可以制得[[对甲苯磺酰氯|对甲苯磺酰氯]]。后者用在[[亲核取代反应|亲核取代反应]]中，也用作醇羟基的[[保护基|保护基]]。

: ''p''-CH<sub>3</sub>C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>SO<sub>3</sub>Na + PCl<sub>5</sub> → ''p''-CH<sub>3</sub>C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>SO<sub>2</sub>Cl

对甲苯磺酸与脱水剂[[五氧化二磷|五氧化二磷]]混合加热后可生成对甲苯磺酸酐<ref>{{OrgSynth |title = ''p''-Toluenesulfonic Anhydride |collvol = 4 |collvolpages = 940 |year = 1963 |author = L. Field and J. W. McFarland |prep = cv4p0940}}</ref>。

对甲苯磺酸的用途还有：催化[[醇|醇]]上[[二氢吡喃|二氢吡喃]]保护基、羧酸的[[酯化|酯化]]<ref>{{cite journal |title = Esterification of oleic acid by methanol catalyzed by p-toluenesulfonic acid and the cation-exchange resins K2411 and K1481 in supercritical carbon dioxide|author=Corinne Vieville , Zephirin Mouloungui , Antoine Gaset|journal=Ind. Eng. Chem. Res. |year=1993 |volume=32 |issue=9 |pages=2065–2068|doi=10.1021/ie00021a031|url=http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ie00021a031}}</ref><ref>{{OrgSynth | author = Furuta, K. Gao, Q.-z.; Yamamoto, H. | title = Chiral (Acyloxy)borane Complex-catalyzed Asymmetric Diels-Alder Reaction: (1R)-1,3,4-Trimethyl-3-cyclohexene-1-carboxaldehyde | year = 1998 | collvol = 9 | collvolpages = 722 | prep = cv9p0722}}</ref>和[[酯交换反应|酯交换反应]]<ref>{{OrgSynth | author = Imwinkelried, R.; Schiess, M.; Seebach, D. | title = Diisopropyl (2S,3S)-2,3-O-isopropylidenetartrate | year = 1993 | collvol = 8 | collvolpages = 201 | prep = cv8p0201}}</ref>；使醛生成[[缩醛|缩醛]]<ref>{{OrgSynth | author = H. Griesser, H.; Öhrlein, R.; Schwab, W.; Ehrler, R.; Jäger, V. | title = 3-Nitropropanal, 3-Nitropropanol, and 3-Nitropropanal Dimethyl Acetal | year = 2004 | collvol = 10 | collvolpages = 577 | prep = v77p0236}}</ref>；作为[[水解|水解]][[蛋白质|蛋白质]]和[[糖蛋白|糖蛋白]]的催化剂<ref>{{cite journal |author=T.-Y. Liu and Y. H. Chang |title=Hydrolysis of proteins with p-toluenesulfonic acid. Determination of tryptophan. |journal=J Biol Chem. |year=1971 |volume=246 |issue=9 |pages=2842-2848 |url=http://www.jbc.org/content/246/9/2842.short |pmid=5102928 |access-date=2012-10-21 |archive-date=2016-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317113745/http://www.jbc.org/content/246/9/2842.short |dead-url=no }}</ref>；催化可用合成二氢嘧啶的[[Biginelli反应|Biginelli反应]]<ref>{{cite journal |author=Tongshou Jin, Suling Zhang,and Tongshuang Li|title=p-TOLUENESULFONIC ACID-CATALYZED EFFICIENT SYNTHESIS OF DIHYDROPYRIMIDINES: IMPROVED HIGH YIELDING PROTOCOL FOR THE BIGINELLI REACTION|volume=32|issue=12|pages=1847-1851|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1081/SCC-120004068|doi=10.1081/SCC-120004068}}</ref>以及金属[[硝酸盐|硝酸盐]]有区域选择性地在[[苯酚|苯酚]]和取代苯酚中酚羟基的邻位进行[[硝化反应|硝化反应]]<ref>{{cite journal |author=V. Anuradha, P.V. Srinivas, P. Aparna, J. Madhusudana Rao |title=p-Toluenesulfonicacid catalyzed regiospecific nitration of phenols with metal nitrates |journal=Tetrahedron Lett. |volume=47 |issue=28 |year=2006 |pages=4933–4935 |url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0040403906009270 |doi=10.1016/j.tetlet.2006.05.017 |access-date=2012-10-24 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924160159/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0040403906009270 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 制备 ==
工业上通过用浓硫酸对[[甲苯|甲苯]]发生[[磺化|磺化]]制取对甲基苯磺酸。制得的对甲苯磺酸中常含有[[苯磺酸|苯磺酸]]和[[硫酸|硫酸]]杂质，可通过将不纯样品在浓[[盐酸|盐酸]]中[[重结晶|重结晶]]后，[[共沸|共沸]]干燥得到纯品<ref>{{cite book |author = Perrin, D. D. and Armarego, W. L. F. |title = Purification of Laboratory Chemicals |publisher = Pergamon Press |location = Oxford |year=1988}}</ref>。

